draw((-3,0)--(8,0));
draw((0,-1)--(0,8));
draw((0,0)--(7,2),dashed);
draw((0,0)--(-2,7),dashed);

dot("$7 + 2i$", (7,2), E);
dot("$-2 + 7i$", (-2,7), N);
[/asy]

Thus, the image of $7 + 2i$ is $i(7 + 2i) = \boxed{-2 + 7i}.$

